<title>
MAF Sensor Inspection
</title>
<s1 page = "2">
<ptxt>
Remove MAF and IAT sensor. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A1306021"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1 page = "2">
<ptxt>
Connect MAF and IAT sensor (1) to 12 V battery (2) and voltmeter (3) as shown in figure.
</ptxt>
<figure page = "2">
<graphic graphicname = "I8T401132028.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "64.665mm" ver = "01" gw = "239" gh = "167"/>
</figure>
</s1>
